Start the browser server:

```bash
npx camofox-browser@latest
```

Add CamoFox MCP to your MCP client:

```json
{
  "servers": {
    "camofox": {
      "type": "stdio",
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "camofox-mcp@latest"],
      "env": {
        "CAMOFOX_URL": "http://localhost:9377"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

